      .row
        h2 How to do it...
        h3 Getting your latest tweet.
        p
          | Add&nbsp;
          code http://www.lasttweetpng.com/:username/tweet/latest.png
          | &nbsp;to your&nbsp;
          code img
          | &nbsp;tag in your HTML, where&nbsp;
          code :username
          | &nbsp;is your twitter username.
        p
          | Example: This code,&nbsp;
          code &lt;img src="http://www.lasttweetpng.com/joshfinnie/tweet/last.png" alt="@joshfinnie's latest tweet."&gt;
          | , produces this image:
        p.text-center
          img(src='http://www.lasttweetpng.com/joshfinnie/tweet/last.png', alt='')
